"Ballistic Attack"
        This allows the psionicist to hurl a small object at superhigh
        speeds into a target.  The object must contain within it a
        spark of mental energy implanted for the psionicist to contact.
        The guild shop sells rocks with this special modification made
        to them for 5 coins apiece.  The power is the newbie psionicist
        attack power, doing a small amount of damage but being extremely
        cheap in SP and having a very low concentration time.
 
Command:  *THIS POWER HAS BEEN REMOVED*
